Basic Entities uses in Body
------------------------------------


- line break            <br>
- blank space            &nbsp;
- pre-formatted        <pre>
  It can present the content exactly as defined in source code.
  It will not distrub the formats.
 
Syntax:
  <pre>
    .... your content....
  </pre>



  - Address container :   <address>
  It is used to define contact details.
  It makes the address SEO friendly.




  Summary:
1. line break
2. blank space
3. pre-formatted
4. code
5. variable
6. sample text
7. address


2. Fieldset and Legend
    - Fieldset sets a frame for content.
    - Legend sets a caption for frame.

 Syntax:
    <fieldset>
        <legend> title </legend>
        ........your content.........
    </fieldset>


     
     
     
                       Various Containers for Presenting Text
1. Data list with terms and definitions

    - Data list is defined with <dl>
    - Data list contains terms defined with <dt>
    - Data list contains definition defined with <dd>

Syntax:
    <dl>
        <dt> Term </dt>
        <dd> Definition</dd>
    </dl>
